@lisp
(define (make-queue)
  (let ((front-ptr @r{…} )
        (rear-ptr @r{…} ))
    ⟨@var{definitions of internal procedures}⟩
    (define (dispatch m) @r{…})
    dispatch))
@end lisp

Complete the definition of @code{make-queue} and provide implementations of the
queue operations using this representation.
@end quotation

